data.title: Edward Garnier KC and Jennie Gillies join 4 Pump Court
data.meta_description: 4 Pump Court is delighted to announce that Lord Garnier KC has joined 4 Pump Court from One Brick Court with effect from 1st May 2019. Edward has a broad commercial practice spanning defamation and privacy, malicious falsehood, contempt and related media law cases, corporate crime and international human rights.
